          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Man, what an absolute miserable experience. I knew I was in for a rough ride when after fighting my first group of enemies, I immediately turned the game off and decided that doing my laundry was a better use of my time. If you really want a rhythm-based first-person shooter, while it isn’t available on the Switch, you’d be better off playing ",
